content: odilitime: Merged 10 PRs this week, including a major refactoring effort to optimize memory fetching (PR #2135, +115k/-50k lines) and a significant version preparation PR (#2171, +272k/-147k lines). Consistently active every day with 75 commits across nearly 18,000 files, while also providing substantial code review support with 52 reviews (17 approvals). Fixed several issues including postinstall scripts (PR #1872), environment defaults (PR #1999), and added new features like Hyperfy support (PR #1896, +273/-24 lines).
